'''Vidyasagar Mahavidyalaya''', established in 1998,<ref>{{cite web|title=Vidyasagar Mahavidyalaya in Hooghly district | url=http://www.hooghlydistrict.info/vidyasagar-mahavidyalaya-hooghly-district.html|}}</ref> is an undergraduate college in [[Masat]] of [[Hooghly district]], [[West Bengal]], India. It is affiliated with the [[University of Calcutta]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Affiliated College of University of Calcutta | url=http://www.caluniv.ac.in/Affiliated%20college/College_frame.htm|}}</ref>


==Departments==

===Arts and Commerce===

*Bengali
*English
*History
*Political Science
*Education
*Commerce

